1
00:00:33,880 --> 00:00:34,640
MANTI

2
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:05,200
Hi!

3
00:01:16,360 --> 00:01:19,000
The change clip you gave me

4
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,200
is stuck in my heart.

5
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:25,039
Those scenes of love

6
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:28,800
All appear in front of me

7
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:32,240
The beginning and end of the song

8
00:01:32,240 --> 00:01:35,840
represents my longing.

9
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:41,840
Finish this part.

10
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:46,759
Thank you.

11
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:57,560
Mr. Cao.

12
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:58,800
Hi.

13
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,480
Why are you here?

14
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:02,680
I came here often when I first came to Shenzhen.

15
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,240
Xiao Tian, long time no see. Boss.

16
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,240
This is for you.

17
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,039
Thank you.

18
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:08,800
Sit.

19
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,000
Sit down.

20
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:14,200
I still listen to your show.

21
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,560
You're getting more and more stylish.

22
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,400
Thank you for taking care of me.

23
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,640
Tony is just like you.

24
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,440
He used to sing at my place.

25
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:26,040
Now I'm a big broadcaster, a celebrity.

26
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,800
Really?

27
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:28,760
Why would I lie to you?

28
00:02:28,760 --> 00:02:30,680
He's been working for me since he came to Shenzhen.

29
00:02:30,880 --> 00:02:32,320
He has to go to many places every day.

30
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,160
Teach piano in the morning.

31
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:34,840
In the afternoon, you were a wedding receptionist.

32
00:02:35,040 --> 00:02:37,320
I also worked as a guide in an instrument store and a bookstore.

33
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,920
Anyway, I did everything.

34
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,920
I worked very hard.

35
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,240
The instrument room you're using now

36
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,640
used to be his room.

37
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,760
One time, he forgot to bring the key.

38
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,800
I flipped the window in the middle of the night and was found by the security guard.

39
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:55,640
Now, I've made it.

40
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:00,000
Miaomiao is a good singer.

41
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,800
If there's a chance, help her.

42
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,320
You guys talk.

43
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:08,320
I'm leaving.

44
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,120
Thank you, boss.

45
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,840
Did you write that song?

46
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:14,960
Yes.

47
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,600
What do you think?

48
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,160
Not good, right?

49
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:26,360
Do you have time

50
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,680
Do you have time to create?

51
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,360
Do you plan to stay at the radio station

52
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,680
and find a full-time job?

53
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:37,040
After you settle down,

54
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:39,000
your life will be less stressful.

55
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:40,440
But

56
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:43,000
you should have thought about it.

57
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,360
Once it stabilizes,

58
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:48,120
I might give up writing.

59
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,520
The mission the school assigned me

60
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,680
is very difficult.

61
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,080
The first part

62
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,840
Mr. Zhang, Mr. Wang, Mr. Li

63
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,840
will be in charge.

64
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:13,280
The second part

65
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,000
Mr. Tan, Ms. Song, Ms. Xu

66
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,560
will be in charge.

67
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,959
Be careful.

68
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,320
Don't let me down.

69
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,360
What about you?

70
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:24,480
Let's talk about the math competition.

71
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:28,680
The judge will check the time.

72
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,640
The other mentors can dismiss.

73
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,360
This is the list.

74
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,200
Are you a judge too?

75
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,400
I didn't see Chen Jiawei.

76
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,480
Chen Jiawei.

77
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,600
The one we recommended to you before.

78
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,840
The one you mentioned before, right?

79
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,760
I paid special attention to him.

80
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,320
But he didn't sign up.

81
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,560
That's impossible.

82
00:05:04,960 --> 00:05:06,600
Did he give you the application form?

83
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,800
I don't remember.

84
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:15,760
Sir, can we still sign up now?

85
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,120
Can you give him a chance?

86
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,360
He's really good.

87
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,320
Okay.

88
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,640
Please sign him up.

89
00:05:23,680 --> 00:05:24,600
I'm looking forward to it too.

90
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:26,000
I don't know what kind of person he is.

91
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,360
Thank you, Director.

92
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,800
Do you know what award he won in college?

93
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,520
I don't know. How can I remember?

94
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,040
I don't remember anything.

95
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,600
Okay, then remind him

96
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,320
to read the notice online.

97
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,520
Yes, Director.

98
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,120
How could he not remember?

99
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,960
Is there a reason?

100
00:05:56,280 --> 00:05:57,159
Do you know?

101
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:21,440
Get out.

102
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,640
To the store.

103
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,640
Are you busy these days?

104
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,840
I'm fine. I've been busy

105
00:06:27,840 --> 00:06:29,280
and other part-time jobs.

106
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:33,440
Did you forget the math competition

107
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:35,120
Did you forget to sign up?

108
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:43,159
I've been busy these days.

109
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,400
I forgot about it.

110
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,520
I knew it.

111
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:47,480
It's okay. I've signed up for you.

112
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,400
The interview is already online.

113
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,560
You know our school's address, right?

114
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,840
It's in the application form I sent you last time.

115
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:56,880
Check it.

116
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:13,320
It's in the application form.

117
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,680
Miao is really good at cooking.

118
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,440
If you want to come here for a free meal,

119
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,520
You're welcome.

120
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,000
This is your canteen.

121
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:33,920
I'm going to work now.

122
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,960
My boss told me to go early today.

123
00:07:39,840 --> 00:07:41,880
Why are you blocking the door? Let's go.

124
00:07:43,159 --> 00:07:44,560
It's not the time for outdoor activities.

125
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,640
You didn't even light it.

126
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,000
I'm sorry.

127
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,600
I forgot.

128
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,440
Not really.

129
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,760
I just don't want to participate.

130
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,360
Why?

131
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:10,000
I'm not interested.

132
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,040
I don't believe it.

133
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,880
This excuse

134
00:08:13,880 --> 00:08:15,960
used this excuse many years ago.

135
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,720
Reason is invalid. Change another one.

136
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,880
Don't you think math is a failure?

137
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,600
If I have time,

138
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,840
it's better for me to take two more orders.

139
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,600
Chen Jiawei.

140
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:31,800
It's been years.

141
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,480
you've changed.

142
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:35,400
What about me?

143
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,919
You don't seem to care about your future at all.

144
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,960
I've always been fine with it.

145
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,760
If it doesn't matter,

146
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,760
I wouldn't have been recommended to the Mathematics Department.

147
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,360
If they want to recommend me,

148
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,560
I'll go.

149
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,920
Let's not talk about this.

150
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:57,880
I've registered for you anyway.

151
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,800
Remember to go to the interview.

152
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,880
I'm not going.

153
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,080
I told you.

154
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,920
I don't want to go or go.

155
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,600
What's wrong with you?

156
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:09,840
I don't understand.

157
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:12,560
Do you have something more meaningful to do?

158
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,120
No.

159
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,840
I'm just looking after the store and delivering takeout.

160
00:09:19,080 --> 00:09:21,160
Why are you giving up on yourself?

161
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,960
Where's your ambition?

162
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,320
It's my own business whether I work hard or not.

163
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:38,960
I don't want to talk about me anymore.

164
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,400
You won't understand anyway.

165
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,680
Just leave me alone.

166
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:51,000
Do you think I want to control you?

167
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,600
Chen Jiawei.

168
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,400
Every time I see you like this, I get angry.

169
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,240
I must be crazy.

170
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,160
I can't forget someone like you.

171
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,880
Rule 11 of Growing Worries.

172
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,320
The feeling of liking someone

173
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,640
is self-indulged.

174
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,840
Self-torture.

175
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:33,200
Is she confessing her love?

176
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:37,320
I think

177
00:10:37,880 --> 00:10:39,640
Tan Shutong is too tough.

178
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,240
It's really bad for you to eavesdrop at the door.

179
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,520
I'm not the only one listening.

180
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,080
She must be angry.

181
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,880
They're hiding outside so loud.

182
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:49,360
What can I do?

183
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,960
And I'm already late for work.

184
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,480
Just tell me if you want me to give you a ride. Let's go.

185
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,240
Fancy. How many times has it been?

186
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,600
Ms. Song, I send you to work without asking for anything in return.

187
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,960
Aren't you going to apply for a modeling in Shenzhen?

188
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,760
The second time. Thank you.

189
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:16,800
The reason is that Lin Haoran's house has a new car.

190
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,960
Aren't you going to experience which car is better?

191
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,080
I'll buy it later.

192
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,480
Move your head back.

193
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,640
You're too shameless. You're blocking my mirror.

194
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,040
Don't touch the driver at any time.

195
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:33,440
Be a decent citizen.

196
00:11:35,520 --> 00:11:36,320
By the way,

197
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:38,920
what happened to Wei today?

198
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,480
He said he's not interested in math.

199
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,400
Even I don't believe it.

200
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,480
The word "Lian" is good.

201
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,040
it means you finally

202
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,720
your intelligence level.

203
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:47,840
To be honest,

204
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:52,720
do you want to know or do you want to help Tan Shu Tong?

205
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,680
Of course.

206
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:56,360
Why do you ask?

207
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,480
Is that important?

208
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,440
What if you want to know?

209
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,440
I can tell you.

210
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,920
If Tan Shu Tong wants to know,

211
00:12:01,920 --> 00:12:03,160
let her ask Wei.

212
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,720
Let them

213
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,160
should be solved by them.

214
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,240
What's wrong?

215
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,440
Do you think your boss

216
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,760
is very handsome today?

217
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,840
Please be a good driver.

218
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,560
Don't threaten the safety of passengers

219
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:19,120
because of narcissism.

220
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,880
You were defeated by my maturity.

221
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,320
Angry.

222
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,800
That's a good idea.

223
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,040
But you may have forgotten

224
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,280
there is a boy who loves sharing.

225
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:31,560
called Lin Haoran.

226
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,160
What's wrong? I'm late.

227
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,680
I'm going to be late.

228
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,920
Lin Gou.

229
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:43,320
If someone asks you about Wei,

230
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,520
don't tell anyone.

231
00:12:45,240 --> 00:12:48,800
Especially the girls in the next dorm.

232
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,920
Chen, don't worry.

233
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,440
Who am I?

234
00:12:57,760 --> 00:12:59,880
My mouth is as reliable as 502.

235
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,000
Do you want to die?

236
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:07,120
You said you were going to be late.

237
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:12,280
MENU.

238
00:13:17,760 --> 00:13:19,200
Pick up. I can't see the GPS.

239
00:13:21,160 --> 00:13:23,880
MENU.

240
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,440
Hello?

241
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,000
Where are you?

242
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:28,920
Mr. Cao, I'm sorry.

243
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,400
I was late.

244
00:13:30,520 --> 00:13:32,360
There should be five minutes left.

245
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:32,800
MENU.

246
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:34,200
It'll be too late if you come.

247
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,800
Can you talk now?

248
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:39,320
Yes.

249
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:42,080
I listened to your demo again.

250
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,520
It’s not bad.

251
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,960
The arrangement is too rough.

252
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,480
It's a totally saliva song.

253
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,720
If this was sent to the record company,

254
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,400
you would have been killed in the first round.

255
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,920
Have you learned composing?

256
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,560
I learned it in college.

257
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,200
This is not a problem.

258
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,040
It sounds good.

259
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:03,760
I can't stand it.

260
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,880
I tried to change it.

261
00:14:05,640 --> 00:14:06,480
Really?

262
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,680
I'll send it to you later. Listen to it.

263
00:14:09,640 --> 00:14:11,120
Have you made up your mind

264
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,160
Have you decided?

265
00:14:15,480 --> 00:14:17,440
I want to think about it again.

266
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,000
It's not about a full-time job.

267
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,520
It's the 10,000 yuan from the dance troupe.

268
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,720
They already transferred the money to me.

269
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:25,240
I'll transfer it to you on WeChat.

270
00:14:26,520 --> 00:14:27,640
But I think...

271
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,480
But what?

272
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:31,480
You don't have money, time and energy now.

273
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:34,160
You need to focus on one thing to create.

274
00:14:36,600 --> 00:14:38,160
And those dancers.

275
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,720
They won't remember even if they don't pay a price.

276
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,360
Besides,

277
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:44,640
they messed up my show. I haven't settled the score.

278
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:50,080
500 meters ahead, we're arriving at our destination.

279
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,680
We're here. Come up quickly.

280
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,440
What did he say?

281
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,600
What 10,000 yuan?

282
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:14,240
I recorded the recording of the dance troupe bullying Wu Di.

283
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:16,320
They wanted to give me 10,000 yuan to delete it.

284
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,440
Are you kidding me?

285
00:15:18,480 --> 00:15:19,560
