524
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,240
Of course.

525
00:29:29,680 --> 00:29:31,600
There are always some regrets when you're young.

526
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:35,200
This is also a kind of beauty given by life.

527
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,040
Enjoy the moment.

528
00:29:47,480 --> 00:29:49,000
